## Decisions Made
- Resolve is idempotent when the open/ file is missing but resolved/ exists — returns `changed: false, replayed: true` rather than error.
- The _index.md update is best-effort (only modified if the file exists) and uses simple string-replace to insert a new row before "## Resolved Gates".
- Both string options (just labels) and dict options ({label, description}) are accepted in the open payload's options list.

